{"tid":1324644,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位和理非入一入黎，星期六一齊文宣遍地開花","createTime":"2019-07-16T15:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T15:33:42.000Z","uid":280725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6228bcbc450b775fe7544e7140deeba17e5830f","tid":1324644,"uid":280725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:25:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">想星期六去自己個區連儂牆坐底擺booth同人辯論</span><br />\n類似呢D咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SGWXjN6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSGWXjN6.png&h=aa1e5c47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔使攞枱都得<br />\n坐係地下擺紙皮牌係隔離同人講命題同規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真我真係和理非到走火入魔<br />\n不過我仲係覺得只要可以說服一個人都值得<br />\n大家覺得自己唔會拗輸比人可以一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊星期六出黎自己個區連儂牆<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比大家見到公理何在</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記住唔好人身攻擊 要真係理論<br />\n同見有藍絲激動 可以幫口說理<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但千其唔好激動過佢</span><br />\n呢個都係形象工程<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千其唔好主動郁手</span></strong>"},{"pid":"760075afe1484d30648652efd9496bd01a1cbb96","tid":1324644,"uid":280725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:27:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecea7a61c765ba8aab601803d33473d32407402","tid":1324644,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4b2a450c529d17cb3d756337cab98c087b0c37cf","tid":1324644,"uid":280725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:31:30.000Z","msg":"唔一定星期六先開始<br />\n只係我星期六一定會出黎"},{"pid":"47fd814858ac0c38cb648d689c27b08945b4f1e0","tid":1324644,"uid":280725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n今次文宣一定要得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}